  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Using the Yamanaka clans propensity for mental exploration, you are able to enhance the mental receptors of a willing creature you can touch, within range. Pick one between Intelligence, Wisdom and Charisma. For the duration, the affected creature gains proficiency in the chosen ability scores saving throw. A creature that already has proficiency in the chosen score instead gains a +2 bonus to saving throws made with said score.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3. If this jutsu is cast at A-Rank, you may select +1 additional creature.</p>",
